<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_99" id="49v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_99_r1l20">Matheıs <expan>Scharffemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_99_r1l21"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Matheıs als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe ewch <expan>ankome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l22">ſey daʒ wır eẅch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>denken</expan> <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ Jr bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſchede<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l23"><expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeyt etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l24"><expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ wır dauon niht gehört <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l25">des <expan>v<ex>er</ex>wıſſen</expan> . Vnd <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> auch ʒu <expan>dıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r1l26">nicht ʒe <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn gut . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_99" id="49v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Matheis <expan>Scharffemberg<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Matheis, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch
                                                  <expan>ankome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, daz wir ewch
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>denken</expan>
<expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> daz ir bey
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>schede<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> seyt etc., das
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch
                                                  <expan>wiss<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz wir davon niht
                                                gehört <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> und
                                                  <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewch des
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>wissen</expan> und
                                                  <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> auch zu
                                                  <expan>dis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> mit ewch nicht ze
                                                  <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn gut.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
